<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>语言：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>spoken / written language</strong>
口语/书面语</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>body / sign language</strong>
身势语/手语</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>master a language</strong> 
掌握一门语言</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We did not speak the local language.
我们不会说当地的语言。</p><footer>2020江苏</footer></div></div>